{"id": "1245462989562183690", "channel_id": "1245462989562183690", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "H7-10打卡茜亞的時候沒有出現萊克的特殊卡，我還以為這就是困難之所以困難的原因。\n結果下一關H7-11就全程跟我一起打艾爾瓦了。\n\n萊克先生他沒有輸！他追上來了！", "timestamp": "2024-05-29T19:45:16.295000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1245462989910577283", "filename": "2024-05-30-03-15-51.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 225341, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1245462989562183690/1245462989910577283/2024-05-30-03-15-51.jpg?ex=6a00378c&is=69fee60c&hm=9ebdfc4daf1783a2f6cc27886986a595a11b10439dae31d115e2427a9498a5ae&"}, {"id": "1245462990208368651", "filename": "2024-05-30-03-16-00.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 95351, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1245462989562183690/1245462990208368651/2024-05-30-03-16-00.jpg?ex=6a00378c&is=69fee60c&hm=f3bc73658802ec7d52324dac0534a84a171e7955be9bfaba9380ac9e2b53d19a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1245462989562183690", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」萊克雖然會遲到，但他從不缺席", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
